                  </persName>
               
            .</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17971025-22-person201">
                  THOMAS
                   MARSHALL
               <interp inst="t17971025-22-person201" type="surname" value="MARSHALL"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17971025-22-person201" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17971025-22-person201" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn. - I am a <rs id="t17971025-22-viclabel112" type="occupation">cheese-monger</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17971025-22-victim200 t17971025-22-viclabel112"></join> in <placeName id="t17971025-22-crimeloc113">Spital-fields</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17971025-22-crimeloc113" type="placeName" value="Spital-fields"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17971025-22-crimeloc113" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17971025-22-off110 t17971025-22-crimeloc113"></join>. On the 26th of September, about eight o'clock at night, I saw the prisoner passing backwards and forwards in the street; the bacon hung at the door, and I and another laid wait for him; he came to it several times, and at last he took it off the hook and went away with it; I stopped him, and gave charge of him.</p>
               <p>Cross-examined by Mr. Alley. Q. This was at night, and dark? - A. Yes.</p>
               <p>Q.Do you mean to swear that that is the man that took the bacon? - A. Yes, that is the man.</p>
               <p>Q.What coloured coat had he on? - A. A whitish coat on.</p>
               <p>Q. Did you never say it was a man in a blue coat? - A. No; there was a man in a blue coat with him.</p>
               <p>Q. You might have prevented the these if you pleased, by taking in the bacon? - A. Yes.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17971025-22-person202">
                  JOHN
                   GREEN
               <interp inst="t17971025-22-person202" type="surname" value="GREEN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17971025-22-person202" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17971025-22-person202" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn. - I saw the prisoner take the bacon off the hook, and go away with it.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence. I am entirely innocent of the fact.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17971025-22-person203">
